      • SensorOutput

        public SensorOutput​(CharSequence equipmentId,
                    Long windowStart,
                    Long windowEnd,
                    Double averageTemperature,
                    Double maxTemperature,
                    Double minTemperature,
                    Integer sensorCount,
                    CharSequence unit,
                    CharSequence location,
                    Long processingTime,
                    Double anomalyScore)
        All-args constructor.
        Parameters:
        equipmentId - Identifier for the equipment
        windowStart - Window start time in milliseconds
        windowEnd - Window end time in milliseconds
        averageTemperature - Average temperature over the window
        maxTemperature - Maximum temperature in the window
        minTemperature - Minimum temperature in the window
        sensorCount - Number of sensors aggregated
        unit - Measurement unit
        location - Location of the equipment
        processingTime - When this aggregation was processed
        anomalyScore - Optional anomaly detection score
